    <li>National Women in Engineering Day - 23 June 2015 - a day dedicated to raising the profile and celebrating the achievements of women in engineering - http://www.wes.org.uk/nwed</li>
    <li>For more information about the Inspire Engineering days, visit <a href="http://www.ltmuseum.co.uk/learning/schools/key-stage-3">www.ltmuseum.co.uk/learning/schools/key-stage-3</a></li>
